# Copied wasm (Landing Zone Wizard) — prebuild copies from react/src/landingzone/wasm
**/desktop/public/libjsonnet.wasm
# Standalone react dev server — predev copies these into public/ (see react/scripts/copy-static-assets.mjs)
**/react/public/libjsonnet.wasm

# Copied reference architecture library — prebuild copies from ocd/library
**/desktop/public/library/
**/react/public/library/

# Landing Zone Wizard — vendored OCI Operating Entities sources are fetched
# locally via `npm run setup-lz` and NOT committed (they embed upstream OCI
# reference OCIDs). Keep this repo free of any OCIDs / environment identifiers.
**/landingzone/oe/gen/

